Right, I'm trying to engrave ""Elbereth"" to scare this iguana. The action to write seems to be `engrave`, but I can't type `Elbereth` directly. So I tried `engrave`, and then the prompt asks ""What do you want to write with?"" Right, `minus`. I tried that again! I had just used that! And it still defaulted to ""esc""! What is happening? The game seems to be interpreting ""minus"" and the action `-` differently. The parser keeps saying my action is invalid. I'm clearly missing something here.

